9. Mathematical Modeling

9.1 Readiness Index

LRI = α·Cognitive + β·Emotional + γ·Neurological + δ·Temporal + ε·Identity

9.2 Skill Development Curve

d(skill)/dt = k · learning_rate · LRI

9.3 Transfer Matrix

A matrix T where:

T_ij = similarity(micro_skill_i, micro_skill_j)

9.4 Plateau Detection

Using second derivative:

if d²P/dt² ≈ 0 → plateau


